msgid "A MaxCompute project with valid Access ID / Access Key."
msgstr "需要一个已开通的 MaxCompute 项目，并具备有效的 Access ID / Access Key。"

msgid "Applicable scenarios"
msgstr "适用场景"

msgid "At large scale, request higher API quotas to avoid 429/403 throttling."
msgstr "在大规模生产场景中，建议申请更高 API 并发配额以避免 429/403 限流。"

msgid "Automatic tagging and management of large video datasets."
msgstr "海量视频数据自动打标与管理。"

msgid ""
"Autonomous driving systems continuously collect large-scale camera video "
"across road types, traffic conditions, weather, and complex events. These"
" raw videos are critical for model training, scenario mining, data "
"flywheel operations, and evaluation."
msgstr ""
"自动驾驶车辆在研发和运营过程中会持续采集海量摄像头视频数据。这些数据覆盖"
"不同道路类型、交通流、天气光照和复杂事件，是模型训练、场景挖掘、数据闭环"
"和效果评测的重要基础。"

msgid "Background"
msgstr "背景信息"

msgid "Cleanup"
msgstr "资源清理"

msgid "Configure Role ARN for OSS mount access."
msgstr "配置用于 OSS 挂载访问的 Role ARN。"

msgid "Custom image"
msgstr "自定义镜像"

msgid "Data preparation for training and evaluation loops."
msgstr "训练、评测与数据闭环支撑。"

msgid "Dataset clustering and distribution analysis."
msgstr "数据聚类分析与分布评估。"

msgid ""
"Default DPE runtime includes Python but not FFmpeg. Stage-1 frame "
"extraction requires FFmpeg binaries."
msgstr ""
"默认 DPE 运行时仅包含 Python，不包含 FFmpeg；阶段一抽帧依赖 FFmpeg "
"可执行文件。"

msgid ""
"Default DPE runtime includes Python but not FFmpeg. Stage-1 frame "
"extraction requires FFmpeg binaries. For a quick validation run, you can "
"reuse an existing verified FFmpeg image from the same region. For "
"production, build and publish your own image in the same region as the "
"MaxCompute project, then set ``odps.session.image`` to that image name."
msgstr ""
"默认 DPE 运行时仅包含 Python，不包含 FFmpeg；阶段一抽帧依赖 FFmpeg "
"可执行文件。快速验证时，可以复用同地域已经验证过的 FFmpeg 镜像。生产环境"
"建议自行构建并发布与 MaxCompute 项目同地域的镜像，然后将 ``odps.session."
"image`` 设置为该镜像名称。"

msgid ""
"Make sure the mounted OSS path is correct before submitting the job. For "
"example, if your OSS address is ``oss://oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com"
"/jingxuan-oss-test-hz/``, use ``OSS_ENDPOINT = \"oss-cn-"
"hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\"``, ``OSS_BUCKET = \"jingxuan-oss-test-hz\"``, and"
" ``OSS_PATH = \"\"`` or the subdirectory that contains your videos."
msgstr ""
"提交任务前，请确认挂载的 OSS path 正确。例如，如果你的 OSS 地址是 ``oss:/"
"/oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/jingxuan-oss-test-hz/``，则设置 ``OSS_"
"ENDPOINT = \"oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com\"``、``OSS_BUCKET = \"jingxuan-"
"oss-test-hz\"``，并将 ``OSS_PATH`` 设为 ``\"\"`` 或实际存放视频的子目录。"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

msgid "Dockerfile example:"
msgstr "Dockerfile 示例："

msgid "Environment setup"
msgstr "环境准备与会话创建"

msgid "Extract keyframes from videos with FFmpeg."
msgstr "视频抽帧：通过 FFmpeg 按指定帧率抽取关键帧图片。"

msgid "Generate scene labels using multimodal LLMs."
msgstr "图片打标：调用百炼多模态大模型自动生成场景标签和语义描述。"

msgid "Global parameters:"
msgstr "全局参数配置："

msgid "Long-tail and anomaly scenario discovery."
msgstr "异常事件与长尾场景发现。"

msgid "Prerequisites"
msgstr "前提条件"

msgid "Produce embeddings for retrieval, clustering, and sample mining."
msgstr ""
"向量化：提取 Embedding 向量，形成可用于检索、聚类、样本筛选和分析的统一"
"特征底座。"

msgid ""
"Raw video data is usually unstructured and expensive to curate manually. "
"To improve reuse and retrieval efficiency, the data pipeline should "
"standardize frame-level processing:"
msgstr ""
"然而，原始视频通常缺乏结构化标签，人工筛选和整理成本高，导致高价值样本"
"发现难、数据复用效率低。为提升海量视频数据的管理和利用效率，需要对视频"
"进行帧级理解与标准化加工："

msgid "Required for multimodal labeling and embedding calls."
msgstr "用于多模态打标与向量化模型调用。"

msgid "Requirement"
msgstr "条件"

msgid "Similar-scene retrieval and sample recall."
msgstr "相似场景检索与样本召回。"

msgid "Source videos are stored in a target OSS bucket."
msgstr "原始视频已存储在目标 OSS Bucket 中。"

msgid "Stage 1: frame extraction"
msgstr "阶段一：视频抽帧"

msgid "Stage 2: image labeling"
msgstr "阶段二：图片打标"

msgid "Stage 3: multimodal embedding"
msgstr "阶段三：向量化"

msgid "Stage-1 extraction requires FFmpeg in MaxCompute custom image."
msgstr "阶段一抽帧需要在 MaxCompute 自定义镜像中预装 FFmpeg。"

msgid ""
"Stage-1 extraction requires FFmpeg in a MaxCompute custom image. The "
"image must be available in the same region as the MaxCompute project."
msgstr ""
"阶段一抽帧需要使用包含 FFmpeg 的 MaxCompute 自定义镜像。该镜像必须和 "
"MaxCompute 项目处于同一地域。"

msgid "This tutorial shows an end-to-end distributed implementation on MaxFrame."
msgstr ""
"本方案依托 MaxFrame 的分布式处理能力，实现视频数据的端到端批量处理，帮助"
"将非结构化视频数据转化为可检索、可分析、可复用的数据资产。"

msgid "Video Pipeline: Frame Extraction -> Labeling -> Embedding"
msgstr "视频处理全流程：抽帧 -> 打标 -> 向量化"

msgid "Video understanding and vectorization pipeline"
msgstr "视频理解与向量化处理流程"

msgid "Why custom image?"
msgstr "为什么需要自定义镜像？"

msgid "Workflow"
msgstr "方案核心流程"

msgid "``apply_chunk`` stages run on DPE."
msgstr "``apply_chunk`` 阶段在 DPE 上执行。"

